Global Residential Cleaning Service Market Insights
Residential Cleaning Service Market size was valued at USD 40.7 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 66.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Residential Cleaning Service Market Overview
The global residential cleaning service market was valued at approximately USD 58 billion in 2023 and is expected to reach USD 88 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% from 2023 to 2030. The market has experienced significant growth due to rising demand for professional cleaning services, with consumers looking for convenience and time-saving solutions. The increase in dual-income households and busy lifestyles has propelled the need for residential cleaning services. With growing awareness about hygiene, cleanliness, and maintaining a safe living environment, the market has seen consistent expansion globally.

